{"id":458909,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trainspotting_(movie)","text":"\"Trainspotting\" is a 1996 British crime comedy drama movie. It is based on the novel of the same name by Irvine Welsh. This movie is about heroin addicts in late 1980s Edinburgh. The movie's cast includes Ewan McGregor, Ewen Bremner, Jonny Lee Miller, Kevin McKidd, Robert Carlyle and Kelly Macdonald.\nThis movie was released in February 1996 in the United Kingdom, and July 1996 in the United States.\nA sequel, \"T2 Trainspotting\", released in 2017.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"United_Kingdom","surface_form":"British","offset":26},{"uri":"Crime","surface_form":"crime","offset":34},{"uri":"Comedy","surface_form":"comedy","offset":40},{"uri":"Drama","surface_form":"drama","offset":47},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":53},{"uri":"Novel","surface_form":"novel","offset":79},{"uri":"Trainspotting_(novel)","surface_form":"of the same name","offset":85},{"uri":"Irvine_Welsh","surface_form":"Irvine Welsh","offset":105},{"uri":"Heroin","surface_form":"heroin","offset":139},{"uri":"Edinburgh","surface_form":"Edinburgh","offset":168},{"uri":"Ewan_McGregor","surface_form":"Ewan McGregor","offset":205},{"uri":"Ewen_Bremner","surface_form":"Ewen Bremner","offset":220},{"uri":"Jonny_Lee_Miller","surface_form":"Jonny Lee Miller","offset":234},{"uri":"Kevin_McKidd","surface_form":"Kevin McKidd","offset":252},{"uri":"Robert_Carlyle","surface_form":"Robert Carlyle","offset":266},{"uri":"Kelly_Macdonald","surface_form":"Kelly Macdonald","offset":285},{"uri":"United_Kingdom","surface_form":"United Kingdom","offset":350},{"uri":"United_States","surface_form":"United States","offset":387},{"uri":"Sequel","surface_form":"sequel","offset":404},{"uri":"T2_Trainspotting","surface_form":"T2 Trainspotting","offset":413}]}